				<wikidot:authorName>Genshed</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2643500</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>&quot;Charlie and the Chocolate Factory&quot;, directed by Tobe Hooper, starring Crispin Glover as Willie Wonka.</p> <p>This makes chocolate horrific. Well done. I found myself wondering just what the 'chocolate gods' were: objectively real entities, or the externalized delusions of a reality bender going insane. Congratulations to the Foundation for neutralizing the final boss</p> 
				 	]]>
