				<wikidot:authorName>xFox</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3165790</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>It's about 4 infections, chocolate children, and a fifth, creepy child that claims he's a 30 year old guy. Also, chocolate demons.</p> <p>I hope you enjoy this a little, because I thought the world needs a creepy chocolate cultist who can make chocolates that allow him to possess other people, in this case a poor kid.</p> 
				 	]]>
